snippet.title: maybe: Interactive Stories | The Tyrant's Bodyguard Ep 1
snippet.description:
The Korean Empire is under the rule of a  constitutional monarchy. You receive a mission to protect the Royal Prince. But the prince who is threatened by terrorist attacks has a goal to overthrow the empire...?
.
.
Scenario by Oming / Artwork by YOOROONG, OFFCAR
.

App Store ➤ https://apps.apple.com/us/app/maybe-interactive-stories/id1508286483
